- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image and video reconstruction using event-based cameras. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as event-based cameras are commonly used in robotics applications. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with video reconstruction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper proposes a new optimization method for solving the energy function.
